
       SOLVING GELFLING ADVENTURE
  THIS GAME IS THE NEW HI-RES ADVENTURE
BY  SIERRA  ON-LINE,  SORTA A SEQUEL TO
THE DARK CRYSTAL. BUT EASIER.
 
AT ANY  GIVEN TIME THE  MOST AMOUNT  OF
OPTIONS YOU  HAVE IS 3,  THE THREE  ARE
LISTED ON THE  SCREEN, MOVE THE  CURSOR
DOWN BY HITTING THE SPACE BAR AND PRESS
RETURN WHEN FINISHED CHOSING OPTION YOU
WANT.
 
 OK FROM HERE ON IT WILL BE ALL NUMBERS
FROM 1-3. THIS IS THE FULL SOLUTION  TO
GELFLING ADVENTURE, IT WILL NOT LET YOU
FINISH IN THE LEAST AMOUNT OF MOVES BUT
YOU CAN DO THAT IF YOU FEEL ADVENTUROUS
 
 WHEN YOU SOLVE THE GAME USING THE SOL-
UTION DO NOT  TYPE IN THE NUMBER,  MOVE
DOWN TO THE NUMBER USING THE SPACE BAR.
 
OK...
 
